span><br />\n___________________________________________<br />\n<br />\n明白個遊戲點玩未？？<br />\n<br />\n每個禮拜都咁多手足俾人拉咗，分分鐘坐幾年甚至十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你真係甘心佢地咁努力，然後我地白費曬佢地嘅心機？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有勇氣上街頭勇武<br />\n點解唔敢入機場？</span>"},{"pid":"8f961e97ddd962f35da87fa6eeeff60fee1aba39","tid":1513358,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:53:25.000Z","msg":"831 民陣<br />\n91 機場<br />\n92 三罷 繼續機場"},{"pid":"18301868341cee7068720f002d20f8dc2ae1b8fa","tid":1513358,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:54:00.000Z","msg":"小心支那香港航空有件深藍空姐姓胡x琳，佢肯定會係打報告果類人黎"},{"pid":"51deb93a8130d76ca2fbc07f832416fd924f8ac4","tid":1513358,"uid":281342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O47NtDv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO47NtDv.jpg&h=773f72fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hJGZjLa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhJGZjLa.jpg&h=5120cd1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cOGnhwQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcOGnhwQ.jpg&h=b6d8a035&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZR7d8Dv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZR7d8Dv.jpg&h=db8d1505&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb151fdddea73c4ba493ea032179ddb4fb11eb39","tid":1513358,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:01:14.000Z","msg":"咁你咪叫777答應五大訴求囉，記得缺一不可"},{"pid":"2440d92e1263d6afaeb79d7ded1c523992d3d6e7","tid":1513358,"uid":22701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"18301868341cee7068720f002d20f8dc2ae1b8fa","tid":1513358,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:54:00.000Z","msg":"小心支那香港航空有件深藍空姐姓胡x琳，佢肯定會係打報告果類人黎"},